{"data":[{"date":"16:10 03/07","title":"\u0110\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf Spurs s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng quy\u1ebft chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Harry Kane t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/dong-doi-o-spurs-san-sang-quyet-chien-voi-harry-kane-tai-vong-18.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o CLB, nh\u01b0ng trong tr\u1eadn Anh vs Colombia t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Davinson Sanchez quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m b\u1eaft ch\u1ebft Harry Kane.\r\n</h2><h2>Sanchez s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng k\u00e8m ch\u1eb7t \u0111\u00e0n anh<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi\u1ebfn Tottenham ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 m\u00ecnh, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Davinson Sanchez \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf t\u00e0i n\u0103ng, v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t trong n\u0103m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean gia nh\u1eadp Premier League. \u1ede k\u1ef3 World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1996 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i nh\u1ea5t tham d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Colombia.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam nay, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Nam M\u1ef9 s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi \u0110T Anh cho m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. B\u1edfi v\u1eady v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o CLB c\u00f9ng Harry Kane, Davinson Sanchez s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn trong nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 b\u1eaft ch\u1ebft \u0111\u00e0n anh &ndash; ng\u00f2i n\u1ed5 s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sanchez va Kane trong mau ao Tottenham\" title=\"Sanchez v\u00e0 Kane trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Tottenham\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/dong-doi-o-spurs-san-sang-quyet-chien-voi-harry-kane-tai-vong-18.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Davinson Sanchez quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m b\u1eaft ch\u1ebft Harry Kane d\u00f9 h\u1ecd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i CLB</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 m\u1edbi b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 22 cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Harry Kane l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft anh \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t t\u1ea1i World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 t\u00f4i h\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 khi b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u, khi \u0111\u00f3 b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1eed th\u00e1ch.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1ea1i Tottenham. M\u1ed9t ch\u00e0ng trai tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, nh\u01b0ng ngay khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1eddi CLB \u0111\u1ec3 tham gia nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 t\u1ea1i \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi nhau m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00ecnh b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t sang m\u1ed9t b\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn n\u00e0y. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 \u0110T Colombia c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft&rdquo; &ndash; Davinson Sanchez quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m b\u1eaft ch\u1ebft Harry Kane.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, HLV Gareth Southgate \u0111\u00e3 cho \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Harry Kane ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Tottenham s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/rooney-tuyen-anh-co-the-mo-mong-o-world-cup-nay-421-190252.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/31/rooney-tuyen-anh-co-the-mo-mong-o-world-cup-nay.PNG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/rooney-tuyen-anh-co-the-mo-mong-o-world-cup-nay-421-190252.html\">Rooney: Tuy\u1ec3n Anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u01a1 m\u1ed9ng \u1edf World Cup n\u00e0y</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u \u0111inh v\u1edbi Colombia v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam nay, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Wayne Rooney \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o \u0110T Anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-colombia-vs-anh-1h00-ngay-47-co-den-tay-lieu-co-phat-421-190241.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/Colombia-vs-Anh.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-colombia-vs-anh-1h00-ngay-47-co-den-tay-lieu-co-phat-421-190241.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Colombia vs Anh (1h00 ng\u00e0y 4/7): C\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn tay, li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 ph\u1ea5t?</span><br>\r\nNh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Colombia vs Anh v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018: R\u01a1i v\u00e0o nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i d\u1ec5 th\u1edf, Tam S\u01b0 \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u nh\u1ea5t trong v\u00f2ng 28 n\u0103m qua, t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/southgate-dt-anh-se-khong-bi-loai-soc-nhu-o-euro-2016-469-190250.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/southgate-dt-anh-se-khong-bi-loai-soc-nhu-o-euro-2016.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/southgate-dt-anh-se-khong-bi-loai-soc-nhu-o-euro-2016-469-190250.html\">Southgate: \u0110T Anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i s\u1ed1c nh\u01b0 \u1edf Euro 2016</span><br>\r\nHLV Southgate kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u01a1i v\u00e0o c\u00e1i b\u1eaby t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 2 n\u0103m khi \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Colombia \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; TTVN&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"857","checkdouble":"190283"},{"date":"16:23 03/07","title":"Ajax ch\u1ec9 mua l\u1ea1i Daley Blind v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/12/15/ajax-chi-mua-lai-daley-blind-voi-mot-dieu-kien.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ajax mua Daley Blind c\u1ee7a MU \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 ch\u1ec9 x\u1ea3y ra n\u1ebfu h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 28 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn gi\u1ea3m l\u01b0\u01a1ng. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 Lan kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng g\u00e1nh n\u1ed5i m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u1edf Old Trafford.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ajax \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n mua l\u1ea1i Daley Blind</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDaley Blind ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Ajax trong 6 n\u0103m, t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2008 \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2014. Sau \u0111\u00f3 anh chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Old Trafford v\u00e0o H\u00e8 2014 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 kho\u1ea3ng 16 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ajax mua Daley Blind ch\u1ec9 x\u1ea3y ra v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ajax mua Daley Blind ch\u1ec9 x\u1ea3y ra v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/31/Ajax-mua-Daley-Blind-chi-xay-ra-voi-mot-dieu-kien-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ajax \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n mua l\u1ea1i Blind</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o M.U, nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Blind r\u1ea5t \u0111a n\u0103ng, anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 trung v\u1ec7, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i ho\u1eb7c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m, \u1edf Old Trafford anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1edf t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0y nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00f2n vai.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Mourinho, Blind kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 4 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Blind, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n M.U b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Blind v\u1edbi M.U ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn H\u00e8 2019 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u n\u00e0o cho th\u1ea5y hai b\u00ean s\u1ebd gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Old Trafford \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/day-ben-do-moi-cua-daley-blind-neu-roi-mu-172-190201.html\">Ajax l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m Blind nh\u1ea5t</span>, h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 8 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i H\u00e0 Lan. Theo The Sun, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa v\u1edbi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0y, b\u1edfi v\u1eady kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng anh tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ajax ch\u1ec9 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Blind v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ajax mua Daley Blind c\u1ee7a MU \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 ch\u1ec9 x\u1ea3y ra n\u1ebfu h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 28 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn gi\u1ea3m l\u01b0\u01a1ng. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 Lan kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng g\u00e1nh n\u1ed5i m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u1edf Old Trafford.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Daley Blind\" title=\"Daley Blind\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/15/ajax-chi-mua-lai-daley-blind-voi-mot-dieu-kien.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Ajax, Daley Blind bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ea3m l\u01b0\u01a1ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n Blind \u0111ang nh\u1eadn 120.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n \u1edf M.U, ph\u00eda Ajax ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng t\u1ed1i \u0111a m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 60.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i. Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Ajax c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ea3m 50% l\u01b0\u01a1ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBlind s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. N\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1eef v\u1eefng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i anh ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf M.U. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n anh bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ea3m l\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Old Trafford.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"856","checkdouble":"190284"},{"date":"17:06 03/07","title":"Sao tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p n\u1eb1ng n\u1eb7c \u0111\u00f2i r\u1eddi Sevilla t\u1edbi Arsenal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/sao-tuyen-phap-nang-nac-doi-roi-sevilla-toi-arsenal.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Michael Carrick ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Jesse Lingard, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a M.U \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jesse Lingard \u0111ang tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jesse Lingard l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh M.U. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh ghi t\u1edbi 14 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 5 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o, anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Man \u0111\u1ecf.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Michael Carrick ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Jesse Lingard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Michael Carrick ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Jesse Lingard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/carrick-len-tieng-ca-ngoi-jesse-lingard.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lingard \u0111ang ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o MU v\u00e0 \u0110T Anh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh Lingard \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch 23 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Anh d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m v\u00e0 phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c cao anh \u0111\u00e3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c HLV Gareth Southgate trao cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 6-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Panama, Lingard \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t hay v\u1edbi 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 1 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau khi v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-colombia-vs-anh-1h00-ngay-47-co-den-tay-lieu-co-phat-421-190241.html\" target=\"_blank\">Anh vs Colombia</span> trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8, HLV Gareth Southgate \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh cho ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o M.U. NHM Tam s\u01b0 \u0111ang r\u1ea5t hy v\u1ecdng Lingard c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0a Anh v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Carrick khen ng\u1ee3i Lingard</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Michael Carrick ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Jesse Lingard, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a M.U \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lingard\" title=\"Lingard\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/1529345402644_lc_galleryImage_Soccer_Football_World_Cup.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Carrick khen ng\u1ee3i Lingard</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i g\u1eb7p c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean khi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 15 tu\u1ed5i, \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3 Lingard g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi t\u00f4i \u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00e0 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cS\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a Lingard c\u00f3 kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u th\u0103ng tr\u1ea7m, nh\u01b0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. S\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng Lingard s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u1edf World Cup 2018, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Lingard \u0111ang r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 tin, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a Anh \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"855","checkdouble":"190285"},{"date":"16:19 03/07","title":"Nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n v\u00e0ng cho tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u gi\u1edd \u0111\u1eb9p Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Th\u1ee5y S\u0129","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/nhan-dinh-thuy-dien-vs-thuy-si-va-du-doan-soi-keo-thuy-si-vs-thuy-dien.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u kh\u00f3 xem. Tuy nhi\u00ean, nh\u1eefng ph\u00e2n t\u00edch d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 ra \u0111i\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- <strong>Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n t\u1eeb h\u00f2a t\u1edbi th\u1eafng</strong><br>\r\n- <strong>Nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</strong> (kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 2)<br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n th\u1eafng 2-1<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u: Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Th\u1ee5y S\u0129<br>\r\nTh\u1eddi gian: 21h ng\u00e0y 3/7<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m: S\u00e2n Saint-Petersburg<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTLCA c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn: Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n -0.90*0:0*0.85 Th\u1ee5y S\u0129<br>\r\nTBT c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn: Nhi\u1ec1u -0.89*2*0.82 \u00cdt<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n, soi k\u00e8o, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch TL h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n, soi k\u00e8o, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch TL h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/nhan-dinh-thuy-dien-vs-thuy-si-va-du-doan-soi-keo-thuy-si-vs-thuy-dien.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 21h ng\u00e0y 3/7</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n t\u1eeb h\u00f2a t\u1edbi th\u1eafng</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 n\u1ebfu n\u00f3i chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch World Cup t\u00ednh t\u1edbi l\u00fac n\u00e0y th\u00f4i c\u0169ng l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n. Ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i th\u00f4i, vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua H\u00e0 Lan \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 2 trong b\u1ea3ng, ch\u1ec9 sau Ph\u00e1p c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng khen.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc VCK t\u1ea1i Nga, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd ki\u1ebfn k\u00eau g\u1ecdi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n g\u1ecdi l\u1ea1i Zlatan Ibrahimovic. R\u1ed1t c\u1ee5c, quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Janne Andersson l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf cho th\u1ea5y trong vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 55 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00fang. Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n kh\u00f4ng Ibrahimovic kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng pha x\u1eed l\u00fd c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, nh\u01b0ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 m\u1ea1nh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thuy Dien thang Mexico 3-0\" title=\"Thuy Dien thang Mexico 3-0\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-dau-mexico-03-thuy-dien.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng su\u1ed1t nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 Ibrahimovic, h\u1ecd ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00e0o ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o cao k\u1ec1u v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i theo c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a anh. Nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng Ibra, Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 h\u01a1n khi ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u m\u0169i \u0111a d\u1ea1ng h\u01a1n. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00f9ng Scandinavi t\u1edbi gi\u1edd l\u00e0 mi\u1ec5n ch\u00ea. Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 1-0. T\u1edbi tr\u1eadn v\u1edbi \u0110\u1ee9c, h\u1ecd chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ecbu thua b\u1edfi c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t tuy\u1ec7t h\u1ea3o c\u1ee7a Toni Kroos. Nh\u01b0ng khi b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o th\u1ebf hi\u1ec3m ngh\u00e8o, Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 v\u00f9ng l\u00ean d\u1eef d\u1ed9i. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Mexico 3-0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng F, tr\u00e1nh lu\u00f4n g\u1eb7p Brazil.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Zlatan Ibrahimovic se khong gop mat cung DT Thuy Dien.\" title=\"Zlatan Ibrahimovic s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u00f9ng \u0110T Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/28/thuy-dien-se-choi-tot-hon-khi-khong-con-ibrahimovic.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Thi\u1ebfu Ibrahimovic kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng B\u1eafc \u00c2u</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nG\u1eb7p Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t \u00f4ng l\u1edbn n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xem nh\u01b0 may m\u1eafn v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n. V\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u00f2n m\u1eebng h\u01a1n n\u1eefa khi m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 thi\u1ebfu \u0111i m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t. Tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a Costa Rica 2-2 \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 m\u1ea5t r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 bao g\u1ed3m Stephan Lichtsteiner v\u00e0 Fabian Schar.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u01b0a h\u1ebft, tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1edd b\u00f3ng l\u0103n, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Steven Zuber c\u00f2n l\u00ean c\u01a1n s\u1ed1t v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee7 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c tham d\u1ef1. Thi\u1ebfu \u0111i 3 m\u1eaft x\u00edch tr\u00ean, s\u1ef1 l\u1ed9n x\u1ed9n c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 l\u00e0 d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u1eddi c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ec3 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/granqvist-phat-bieu-ve-ibrahimovic-va-thuy-dien-421-190211.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/24/granqvist-phat-bieu-ve-ibrahimovic-va-thuy-dien.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/granqvist-phat-bieu-ve-ibrahimovic-va-thuy-dien-421-190211.html\">Kh\u00f4ng Ibrahimovic, Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n c\u00f2n \u0111\u00e1 hay h\u01a1n!</span><br>\r\n<span>Granqvist ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ibrahimovic. T\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n tin r\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u0111\u00f4i khi l\u1ea1i gi\u00fap h\u1ecd thi \u0111\u1ea5u hay h\u01a1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i, Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 thi\u1ebfu \u0111i 2 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 Lichtsteiner v\u00e0 Fabian Schar. V\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 s\u1ebd thi\u1ebfu \u0111i ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng, th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh tinh th\u1ea7n. Ngo\u00e0i ra, nh\u1eefng qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea1t, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a Lichtsteiner khi m\u1ea5t \u0111i c\u0169ng l\u00e0 thi\u1ec7t th\u00f2i. Qua \u0111\u00f3, nh\u1ea1c tr\u01b0\u1edfng Forsberg c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n s\u1ebd c\u00e0ng r\u1ea3nh ch\u00e2n h\u01a1n b\u00ean c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f2n \u1edf trung t\u00e2m, m\u1ed9t Johan Djourou n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng l\u00f3ng ng\u00f3ng khi k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Manuel Akanji s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o n\u00ean c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 b\u1ea5t an. H\u1ecd ch\u01b0a k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nhau ph\u00fat n\u00e0o t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 ra sao kh\u00f4ng ai bi\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien dao Mitrovic ghi ban truoc Thuy Si\" title=\"tien dao Mitrovic ghi ban truoc Thuy Si\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/HLV-Mladen-Krstajic-phat-bieu-ve-tran-Serbia-vs-Thuy-Sy-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 \u0111ang b\u1ecb nghi ng\u1edd</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede c\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi, t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 4 b\u00e0n. \u0110\u00f3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ebfn HLV Vladimir Petkovic kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng b\u1edfi \u00f4ng v\u1ed1n \u01b0u ti\u00ean y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 v\u1eefng v\u00e0ng \u1edf h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7. V\u00e0 gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia 54 tu\u1ed5i h\u1eb3n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y lo l\u1eafng khi \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ea7y h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1i c\u00e1ch Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Mexico 3-0 c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn Petkovic tr\u0103n tr\u1edf. B\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o th\u1ebf bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng B\u1eafc \u00c2u \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5. 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng t\u1ec7 ch\u00fat n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ee5y S\u0129 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n thay v\u00ec thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. Nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i, h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n ti\u1ec1m \u1ea9n nhi\u1ec1u n\u1ed7i lo v\u00e0 HLV Petkovic kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n l\u1ea5y s\u1edf \u0111o\u1ea3n ra \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea9y tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi c\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n c\u1ef1c h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1edbi d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111\u1eb7t c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c 2 tr\u00e1i ch\u1eb5n cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea1t m\u1ee9c t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng. Nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng ng\u1edd r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ph\u00e1t sinh \u1edf cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi khi Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 suy gi\u1ea3m kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c tr\u1eadn t\u1edbi c\u00f3 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. <br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- <strong>Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n t\u1eeb h\u00f2a t\u1edbi th\u1eafng</strong><br>\r\n- <strong>Nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</strong> (kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 2)<br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n th\u1eafng 2-1<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t kh\u00e1c</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- T\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 9 (O 9)<br>\r\n- T\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c hi\u1ec7p 1 c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f9ng l\u1eafm l\u00e0 4 (U 4)<br>\r\n- T\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 3 (U 3)<br>\r\n- T\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t hi\u1ec7p 1 c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 1 (U 1)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nLong Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"854","checkdouble":"190286"},{"date":"17:37 03/07","title":"\u0110\u1ee9c ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \"t\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3\" Joachim Loew","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/Low1.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV 58 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng \u0110TQG n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda World Cup 2018 \u1edf Nga.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c, v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c c\u1ea3 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi khi tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf Nga v\u00e0 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/goc-nhin-phai-chang-tuyen-duc-dang-tro-thanh-nhung-nguoi-anh-moi-421-189831.html\" target=\"_blank\">s\u1edbm b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi World Cup 2018 ngay v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng</span> l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau 80 n\u0103m, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ed5 sau hai tr\u1eadn thua nh\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico v\u00e0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Joachim Loew ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c sau th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Joachim Loew ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c sau th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/Low1.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Joachim Loew s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u1ee9ng m\u0169i ch\u1ecbu s\u00e0o m\u1ecdi b\u00faa r\u00ecu ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u1edbi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda n\u00e0y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng Joachim Loew, ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u1ea7n d\u00e0 \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i m\u00f2n b\u1ea3o th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Gi\u1edbi m\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec7u v\u00ec v\u1eady \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c chia tay sau 12 n\u0103m \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb, ho\u1eb7c m\u1ed9t tr\u00e1t sa th\u1ea3i v\u00e0 kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n k\u1ebfch x\u00f9 b\u1ed3i th\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi gia h\u1ea1n th\u00eam 4 n\u0103m c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ng, ho\u1eb7c HLV 58 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c trong \u00eam \u0111\u1eb9p.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng khi theo th\u00f4ng tin ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2022. B\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eefng \u00fd ki\u1ebfn tr\u00e1i chi\u1ec1u, HLV Joachim Loew s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng \u0110TQG n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 qua \u00edt nh\u1ea5t hai gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn n\u1eefa, bao g\u1ed3m Euro 2020 v\u00e0 World Cup 2022 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i Qatar.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">D\u1eabu sao, Joachim Loew \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u00e0m l\u1ea1i t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i Euro 2022 m\u1edf m\u00e0n b\u1eb1ng hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu g\u1eb7p Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 Peru trong th\u00e1ng Ch\u00edn n\u0103m nay.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/joachim-low-thua-nhan-duc-dang-bi-loai-465-189795.html\">HLV Joachim Loew: \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tan-man/joachim-low-ban-linh-xua-cu-cua-tuyen-duc-dau-roi-392-190026.html\">HLV Joachim Loew:  B\u1ea3n l\u0129nh x\u01b0a c\u0169 c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e2u r\u1ed3i?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"853","checkdouble":"190287"},{"date":"17:52 03/07","title":"Carrick n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Jesse Lingard?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/carrick-len-tieng-ca-ngoi-jesse-lingard.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Michael Carrick ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Jesse Lingard, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a M.U \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jesse Lingard \u0111ang tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jesse Lingard l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh M.U. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh ghi t\u1edbi 14 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 5 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o, anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Man \u0111\u1ecf.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Michael Carrick ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Jesse Lingard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Michael Carrick ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Jesse Lingard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/carrick-len-tieng-ca-ngoi-jesse-lingard.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lingard \u0111ang ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o MU v\u00e0 \u0110T Anh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh Lingard \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch 23 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Anh d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m v\u00e0 phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c cao anh \u0111\u00e3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c HLV Gareth Southgate trao cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 6-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Panama, Lingard \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t hay v\u1edbi 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 1 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau khi v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-colombia-vs-anh-1h00-ngay-47-co-den-tay-lieu-co-phat-421-190241.html\" target=\"_blank\">Anh vs Colombia</span> trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8, HLV Gareth Southgate \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh cho ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o M.U. NHM Tam s\u01b0 \u0111ang r\u1ea5t hy v\u1ecdng Lingard c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0a Anh v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Carrick khen ng\u1ee3i Lingard</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Michael Carrick ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Jesse Lingard, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a M.U \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lingard\" title=\"Lingard\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/1529345402644_lc_galleryImage_Soccer_Football_World_Cup.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Carrick khen ng\u1ee3i Lingard</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i g\u1eb7p c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean khi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 15 tu\u1ed5i, \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3 Lingard g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi t\u00f4i \u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00e0 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cS\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a Lingard c\u00f3 kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u th\u0103ng tr\u1ea7m, nh\u01b0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. S\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng Lingard s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u1edf World Cup 2018, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Lingard \u0111ang r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 tin, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a Anh \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"852","checkdouble":"190289"},{"date":"17:10 03/07","title":"Brazil th\u1eb3ng ti\u1ebfn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft: Ch\u1ea5t th\u00e9p quy\u1ec7n l\u1eabn trong nh\u1eefng v\u0169 \u0111i\u1ec7u Samba","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/brazil-thang-tien-tu-ket-chat-thep-quyen-lan-trong-nhung-vu-dieu-samba.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>World Cup 2018 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1n \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u00f4ng l\u1edbn n\u00e0o th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y an to\u00e0n nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i trong chi\u1ec1u n\u1eafng Samara, Brazil mang \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n v\u00e0 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c h\u01a1n b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o \u1edf v\u00f2ng knock-out t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">B\u1ea5t t\u1eadn nh\u1eefng mi\u1ec1n c\u1ea3m x\u00fac d\u00e0nh cho c\u00fa s\u1ed1c b\u1eadt b\u00e3i c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi ngay sau ba tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng, trong khi \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ri\u00eang 209 tri\u1ec7u d\u00e2n c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc b\u00ean kia b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u sung s\u01b0\u1edbng, hoan h\u1ec9, h\u1ea3 h\u00ea v\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, th\u1edf ph\u00e0o nh\u1eb9 nh\u00f5m. Vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh duy nh\u1ea5t t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i 1-7 d\u01b0\u1edbi tay \u0110\u1ee9c trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup cho Brazil c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 thua nh\u1ee5c t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/brazil-thang-tran-world-cup-dau-tien-le-tru-ta-bat-dau-421-189322.html\" target=\"_blank\">L\u1ec5 tr\u1eeb t\u00e0 b\u00f3ng ma v\u1ea9n v\u01b0\u01a1ng su\u1ed1t 4 n\u0103m qua</span> ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n khi Tite d\u1eabn l\u1ed1i c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 ra b\u01b0\u1edbc ra \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng \u1edf Moscow trung tu\u1ea7n th\u00e1ng B\u1ea3y t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y. \u0110\u00fang, Brazil ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd thua Mexico \u1edf World Cup, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i ch\u1eb3ng ph\u1ea3i \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5y th\u00f4i, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng T\u00e2y Ban Nha, B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u00e0 Argentina \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t ch\u1ee9ng minh c\u00e1i g\u00ec c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra h\u1ebft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Neymar v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt ch\u00ednh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Brazil v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018  Ch\u1ea5t th\u00e9p trong v\u0169 \u0111i\u1ec7u Samba h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Brazil v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018  Ch\u1ea5t th\u00e9p trong v\u0169 \u0111i\u1ec7u Samba h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/Brazil-vao-tu-ket-World-Cup-2018--Chat-thep-trong-vu-dieu-Samba-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Neymar t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh, d\u1eabn l\u1ed1i \u0111\u01b0a\u00a0Brazil v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ch\u00f3i l\u1ecdi nh\u1ea5t Brazil trong chi\u1ec1u n\u1eafng Samara ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd, theo c\u00e1ch r\u1ea5t ri\u00eang c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, sau hai tu\u1ea7n l\u1ec5 le l\u00f3i tia s\u00e1ng d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ee7 cho gi\u1edbi m\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec7u kh\u1ea5p kh\u1edfi hy v\u1ecdng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch t\u1ea1m b\u1ee3. Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 tu\u1ea7n l\u1ec5 c\u1ee7a Paris Saint-Germain, c\u1ee7a Kylian Mbappe, c\u1ee7a Edinson Cavani hay th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o Angel Di Maria c\u01a1 m\u00e0, v\u1eady th\u00ec h\u00e0 c\u1edb g\u00ec Neymar c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 ch\u1ee9?<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t g\u00f3c nguy\u00ean b\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a Neymar, \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng s\u1eafc n\u00e9t cho c\u1ea3 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 nh\u00e2n c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a anh xuy\u00ean su\u1ed1t 90 ph\u00fat. 7 c\u00fa s\u00fat v\u00e0 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, 5 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 1 l\u1ea7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, h\u00e0ng t\u00e1 pha ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt d\u00f9 v\u00f4 ngh\u0129a \u0111\u00f4i khi, r\u1ed3i c\u1ea3 5 l\u1ea7n l\u00e0m m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau tri\u1ec7t h\u1ea1 cho \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, c\u1eb1n nh\u1eb1n v\u1edbi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu m\u00e0n \u0111\u00f3ng k\u1ecbch \u0103n v\u1ea1 \u201ct\u1ed1n\u201d anh th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 s\u1ed1 fan h\u00e2m m\u1ed9. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ebf m\u00e0 r\u1ed3i ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 26 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eabn \u0111ang ti\u00ean phong \u0111i \u0111\u1ea7u k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean h\u1eadu Messi \u2013 Ronaldo v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1edbm gi\u00fap n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 Brazil gi\u1ea3i l\u1eddi nguy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/dt-mexico-bi-loai-o-vong-16-doi-noi-am-anh-quinto-partido-466-190263.html\" target=\"_blank\">n\u1ed7i \u00e1m \u1ea3nh \u201cquinto partido\u201d c\u1ee7a Mexico</span> v\u1eabn c\u00f2n v\u1eb9n nguy\u00ean \u0111\u00e2u \u0111\u00e2y, khi h\u1ecd v\u1eabn \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch\u2026 b\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u1eddng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/neymar-den-di-tiem-phong-cung-se-an-va-voi-bac-si-421-190267.html\">Neymar \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111i ti\u00eam ph\u00f2ng c\u0169ng s\u1ebd \u0103n v\u1ea1 v\u1edbi b\u00e1c s\u0129!</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/neymar-tinh-bo-truoc-moi-cao-buoc-an-va-421-190251.html\">Neymar t\u1ec9nh b\u01a1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ecdi c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c \u0103n v\u1ea1</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mexico \u0111\u00e1ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 c\u0169ng th\u1eadt \u0111\u00e1ng tr\u00e1ch</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">El Tri li\u00ean t\u1ee5c ghi danh v\u00e0o c\u00e1c v\u00f2ng chung k\u1ebft v\u00e0 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn h\u1ecd ng\u00e3 ng\u1ef1a ngay h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau m\u00e0n ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u00e0 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng. T\u1edbi gi\u1edd, Mexico ch\u01b0a th\u1eafng n\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn knock-out n\u00e0o b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean chu\u1ed7i k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c bu\u1ed3n 7 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 c\u00e1c k\u1ef3 World Cup.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Brazil vs Mexico\" title=\"Brazil vs Mexico\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/brazil-thang-mexico-de-vao-tu-ket-world-cup-2018-6fba3fe7.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mexico t\u00ednh \u0111\u00e1nh ph\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u Brazil nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea5t th\u00e0nh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Brazil m\u1ea1nh th\u1eadt nh\u01b0ng Mexico c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 n\u00ean bi\u1ebft t\u1ef1 tr\u00e1ch m\u00ecnh m\u00e0 th\u00f4i, v\u00ec t\u00e2m l\u00fd \u00e1p l\u1ef1c hay \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 5 ng\u00e0y, th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9c ch\u1ee7 quan sau 2\u00a0chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ra qu\u00e2n tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 b\u1ea1i t\u01b0\u1edbng g\u1ecdi t\u00ean nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. M\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n thay v\u00ec th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i 0-3 d\u01b0\u1edbi tay Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng thay v\u00ec nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng, Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 thay v\u00ec Brazil, v\u1edbi 4 b\u1eadc tr\u00ean BXH FIFA ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd l\u00e0 kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch xa v\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Mexico nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c th\u1ea7n t\u1ed1c v\u00e0 tr\u1ef1c di\u1ec7n, v\u1edbi xu h\u01b0\u1edbng pressing t\u1eeb xa c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nh\u1eb1m t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 s\u1edbm. 20 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, El Tri ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng 12 l\u1ea7n trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba c\u1ee7a Selecao tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd mon men l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 \u1edf ph\u00eda c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n. Neymar b\u1ebf t\u1eafc v\u00e0 l\u1ea1c l\u00f5ng, Gabriel Jesus ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 c\u00e1i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh \u1edf Man City trong khi Coutinho b\u1ecb nh\u1eefng t\u00e1n s\u1eafc xanh l\u00e1 nu\u1ed1t ch\u1eedng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng c\u1ea3 Dani Alves v\u00e0 Marceloa v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, Brazil \u201cph\u1ebf\u201d lu\u00f4n \u0111\u00f4i c\u00e1nh, bi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang t\u1eeb th\u1ebf m\u1ea1nh tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. Filipe Luis b\u1ecb Hirving Lozano qu\u1ea7n th\u1ea3o b\u00ean h\u00e0nh lang bi\u00ean tr\u00e1i trong khi \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n b\u00ean kia, Fagner \u0111\u00e1ng l\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecb thay ra ch\u1ec9 sau n\u1eeda ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u khi n\u0103m l\u1ea7n b\u1ea3y l\u01b0\u1ee3t mua vui cho Carlos Vela. Trung t\u00e2m, Andres Guadrado \u0111\u00edch th\u1ecb m\u1ed9t \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 c\u1ea7m tr\u1ecbch th\u1ebf c\u1ee5c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Layun, cau thu so 7 guc xuong san voi lan thu 7 lien tiep DT Mexico bi loai o vong 16 doi.\" title=\"Layun, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 7 g\u1ee5c xu\u1ed1ng s\u00e2n v\u1edbi l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 7 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u0110T Mexico b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/dt-mexico-bi-loai-o-vong-16-doi-noi-am-anh-quinto-partido.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mexico l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 7 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8, cay \u0111\u1eafng nh\u00ecn Brazil v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1eadt kh\u00f4ng may, k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u00e1nh ph\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Mexico \u0111\u00e2u kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 bao m\u1ed9t l\u00e2u \u0111\u00e0i c\u00e1t mong manh v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5 b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 l\u00fac n\u00e0o. D\u01b0\u1edbi b\u1ea7u nhi\u1ec7t 38 \u0111\u1ed9 C \u1edf Samara, l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i th\u1ea7n t\u1ed1c v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t nhanh ch\u00f3ng v\u1eaft ki\u1ec7t s\u1ee9c l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Mexico. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ph\u1ea7n th\u01b0\u1edfng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Osorio h\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 ch\u1eb3ng t\u1ea1o ra n\u1ed5i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, s\u1eafc n\u00e9t n\u00e0o h\u1ebft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p Brazil: Ch\u1ea5t th\u00e9p quy\u1ec7n l\u1eabn trong nh\u1eefng v\u0169 \u0111i\u1ec7u Samba</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, ch\u00ea tr\u00e1ch hay ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Mexico th\u00ec d\u1ec5 khi nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt gi\u0103ng ra c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd, nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 k\u1ebf s\u00e1ch m\u1eabu m\u1ef1c \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn n\u00e0o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Brazil \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. Thiago Silva v\u00e0 Miranda, hai l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1ed5ng tu\u1ed5i ng\u00f3t ngh\u00e9t 70, \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1eddi l\u00e0m n\u00ean c\u1eb7p trung v\u1ec7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t nh\u00ec tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, trong khi Casemiro v\u00e0 Fernandinho thay nhau th\u1ed1ng l\u0129nh trung tuy\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9 \u00e1n treo gi\u00f2 c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao Real Madrid xem ra c\u0169ng kh\u00f3 g\u00e2y \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u cho Tite.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Brazil vs Mexico\" title=\"Brazil vs Mexico\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/165801-4.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Brazil v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng Selecao \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean ti\u00eau \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u00fd mu\u00f4n thu\u1edf. Neymar \u0111\u1ea3m \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, t\u1eeb l\u0129nh x\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn d\u1eaft hay th\u1eadm ch\u00ed s\u1eafm vai m\u1ed3i nh\u1eed, gi\u00fap t\u1eeb Coutinho \u0111\u1ebfn Willian h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i khi thu h\u00fat 2-3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ec1 m\u00ecnh. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Chelsea r\u00ea d\u1eaft th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng k\u00e9m ch\u1ec9 1 l\u1ea7n v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n so v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1ed9ng l\u1ea1i t\u1eeb c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a anh, v\u00e0 r\u1ed3i ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o n\u00ean b\u00e0n th\u1eafng b\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t cho ch\u00ednh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/goc-nhin-neymar-khi-thien-than-luc-ac-quy-421-190242.html\" target=\"_blank\">thi\u00ean th\u1ea7n ki\u00eam \u00e1c qu\u1ef7 Neymar</span>. K\u1ebft li\u1ec5u Mexico v\u00e0 h\u1ea1 m\u00e0n cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u, Roberto Firmino c\u0169ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1ed5n nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">N\u00f3i g\u00ec th\u00ec n\u00f3i, ng\u00e0y ph\u00e1n x\u00e9t cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Tite s\u1ebd h\u1eb5ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u1ecf cho \u0111\u1ebfn tu\u1ea7n l\u1ec5 th\u1ee9 hai c\u1ee7a th\u00e1ng B\u1ea3y s\u1eafp t\u1edbi n\u00e0y. Brazil \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft trong 7 k\u1ef3 World Cup g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y nh\u1ea5t, th\u1ebf n\u00ean h\u1ecd c\u0169ng m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1t m\u1ee9c ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n v\u1ed1n d\u0129 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 4 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc ngay tr\u00ean qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng, gi\u1edd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n v\u1ebb \u0111\u1eb9p mong manh d\u1ec5 v\u1ee1, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed tan n\u00e1t, hi\u1ec7n h\u1eefu \u1edf Brazil n\u1eefa. Neymar v\u1eabn l\u00e0 ngu\u1ed3n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng, l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u00e0u s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t nh\u00f3m r\u1eddi r\u1ea1c c\u00e1c c\u00e1 th\u1ec3. Gi\u1edd, ch\u1ea5t th\u00e9p \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ec7n l\u1eabn trong n\u00e9t \u0111\u1eb9p c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng v\u0169 \u0111i\u1ec7u Samba.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>D\u01b0 \u00e2m ng\u00e0y Brazil v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018:<br>\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-diem-nhan-ngay-neymar-toa-sang-giup-brazil-ha-mexico-20-421-190231.html\">4 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n ng\u00e0y Neymar t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng gi\u00fap Brazil h\u1ea1 Mexico 2-0</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/brazil-20-mexico-xung-danh-nguoi-dan-duong-cua-world-cup-421-190244.html\">Brazil 2-0 Mexico: X\u1ee9ng danh \u201cng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng\u201d c\u1ee7a World Cup</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/goc-nhin-neymar-khi-thien-than-luc-ac-quy-421-190242.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Neymar \u2013 Khi thi\u00ean th\u1ea7n, l\u00fac \u00e1c qu\u1ef7\u2026</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"851","checkdouble":"190290"},{"date":"17:36 03/07","title":"Nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u1eddi cho c\u1ea7u \u0111inh Anh vs Colombia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/nhan-dinh-anh-vs-colombia-va-du-doan-soi-keo-colombia-vs-anh.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Anh vs Colombia c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi ngh\u0129. \u0110T Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u00f3 con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng knock-out World Cup 2018, song h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i d\u00e8 ch\u1eebng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng l\u00e0m n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- <strong>Colombia kh\u00f4ng thua</strong><br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: Colombia th\u1eafng 1-0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u: Anh vs Colombia<br>\r\nTh\u1eddi gian: 1h ng\u00e0y 3/7<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m: S\u00e2n Otkrytiye Arena<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTLCA c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn: Anh 0.89*0:1/4*0-0.94 Colombia<br>\r\nTBT c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn: Nhi\u1ec1u -0.98*2*0.91 \u00cdt<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Anh vs Colombia v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n, soi k\u00e8o, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Anh vs Colombia v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n, soi k\u00e8o, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/nhan-dinh-anh-vs-colombia-va-du-doan-soi-keo-colombia-vs-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Anh vs Colombia 1h ng\u00e0y 4/7</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110T Anh r\u1ea5t mong manh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng C\u0110V Anh n\u00e0o qu\u00ean \u0111i 2 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc n\u01a1i \u0110TQG c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u1ecf b\u00e9 Iceland t\u1ea1i Euro 2016. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia \u0111\u1ec1u nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng cho Tam s\u01b0 ngay c\u1ea3 khi Iceland \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u1edf b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 c\u1ea3 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, Hungary v\u00e0 \u00c1o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Anh vs Colombia c\u0169ng mang t\u1edbi c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c l\u1ea1c quan g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1. \u1ede tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, HLV Gareth Southgate \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n t\u1edbi 9 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i. Anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn c\u00e1ch d\u1ed1c h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i B\u1ec9 qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng G. Song h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 thua 0-1, ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ee9ng nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u1eddi cho c\u1ea7u \u0111inh Anh vs Colombia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u1eddi cho c\u1ea7u \u0111inh Anh vs Colombia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/30/Nhung-du-doan-dong-troi-cho-cau-dinh-Anh-vs-Colombia-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Anh th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t cu\u1ed1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u01b0a n\u00f3i t\u1edbi t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft hay xa h\u01a1n, ngay Colombia c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n v\u1edbi Anh. \u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed3i v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n th\u00ec ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi Tam s\u01b0. Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out ch\u01b0a khi n\u00e0o l\u00e0 d\u1ec5 ch\u1ecbu.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau Euro 2016 t\u1ee7i h\u1ed5, HLV Southgate \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c giao tr\u1ecdng tr\u00e1ch d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0110T Anh. \u00d4ng khuy\u1ebfn kh\u00edch c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n v\u00e0 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i tri\u1ec3n khai b\u00f3ng n\u01a1i ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. Nh\u01b0ng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, nguy c\u01a1 c\u1ee7a Tam s\u01b0 khi ch\u01a1i nh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Panama co duoc ban thang danh du\" title=\"Panama c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng danh d\u1ef1\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/panama.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ebfn Panama c\u0169ng g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho Tam s\u01b0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nPhong c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh na n\u00e1 Man City th\u1eddi Pep Guardiola. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1eebng qu\u00ean ph\u1ea3i t\u1edbi m\u00f9a th\u1ee9 2, Man xanh m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t huy h\u1ebft kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. C\u00f2n Anh, ch\u1ec9 qua 2 tr\u1eadn v\u1edbi c\u00e1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ec3u Panama v\u00e0 Tunisia c\u1ed9ng tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c v\u1edbi B\u1ec9, ch\u00fang ta ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 th\u1eafng 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u, c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Anh cho th\u1ea5y nhi\u1ec1u sai l\u1ea7m, t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 Panama v\u00e0 Tunisia \u00e1p s\u00e1t khung th\u00e0nh. C\u1ea3 hai v\u1edbi tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 c\u00f3 h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 khai th\u00e1c tri\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Tam s\u01b0 nh\u01b0ng Colombia c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-anh-vs-bi-421-189919.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/du-am-anh-vs-bi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-anh-vs-bi-421-189919.html\">Ba tr\u1eadn v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 tuy\u1ec3n Anh v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u1ea9n s\u1ed1!</span><br>\r\n<span>Xoay tua \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u1edbi ch\u00f3ng m\u1eb7t nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i, c\u1ea3 Gareth Southgate v\u00e0 Roberto Martinez \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00ed ph\u1ea1m c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m ch\u1ee9ng th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nColombia r\u1ea5t nguy hi\u1ec3m</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng pressing c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Colombia s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i tr\u1ecdng cho Anh. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 x\u1ee9 s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hu\u00fdt s\u00e1o Juan Cuadrado, ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Chelsea. Nh\u01b0ng khi t\u1edbi Juventus v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110TQG, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh n\u00e0y th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n, Cuadrado c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u01b0\u1edbp b\u00f3ng trong ch\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi d\u1eabn l\u00ean v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3. K\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u00f9ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a James Rodriguez hay Juan Quintero s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng cho t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Cuadrado.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"thu mon Ospina va dong doi Colombia\" title=\"thu mon Ospina va dong doi Colombia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/ospina-phat-bieu-truoc-tran-colombia-vs-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Colombia \u0111ang c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 khi t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng hay ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng, nh\u00e3n quan t\u1ed1t c\u1ea3 Rodriguez v\u00e0 Quintero r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng cho Colombia. C\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 qu\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Radamel Falcao v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111a d\u1ea1ng. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng m\u1ed1i \u0111e d\u1ecda cho h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi 3 tr\u1eadn v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a Anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, Colombia ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i thi\u1ebfu ng\u01b0\u1eddi ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 4 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ea3 2 tr\u1eadn v\u1edbi Senegal v\u00e0 Ba Lan. V\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a Los Cafeteros kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 hoang d\u00e3 m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7y th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng, khoa h\u1ecdc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Noi chien Tottenham Harry Kane - Davinson Sanchez o tran Colombia vs Anh vong 1/8 World Cup 2018\" title=\"N\u1ed9i chi\u1ebfn Tottenham Harry Kane - Davinson Sanchez \u1edf tr\u1eadn Colombia vs Anh v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/colombia-co-noi-gian-trong-doi-tuyen-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Kane\u00a0 h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd b\u1ecb ch\u0103m s\u00f3c g\u1eaft gao b\u1edfi Sanchez</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTunisia v\u00e0 Panama ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ea7m \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n tuy\u1ebfn \u0110T Anh. 5 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Harry Kane th\u1ef1c ra ch\u01b0a n\u00f3i l\u00ean qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1edfi kh\u00f4ng \u00edt ng\u01b0\u1eddi cho r\u1eb1ng anh m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 v\u00f9i d\u1eadp nh\u1eefng k\u1ebb t\u00ed hon y\u1ebfu m\u1ec1m. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nColombia s\u1ebd l\u00e0 thu\u1ed1c th\u1eed li\u1ec1u cao h\u01a1n. \u1ede \u0111\u00f3, Kane s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i Tottenham, Davinson Sanchez kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 ch\u1ecbu. Gi\u1ea3 s\u1eed \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Anh b\u1ecb \u201cb\u1eaft ch\u1ebft\u201d, m\u1ed9t c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t ra: Ai s\u1ebd ghi b\u00e0n cho h\u1ecd? Jesse Lingard v\u00e0 Raheem Sterling \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i m\u01b0\u1eddi m\u01b0\u01a1i v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nColombia l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t t\u1edbi s\u1ef1 to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e1ng m\u01a1 \u01b0\u1edbc. V\u00e0 h\u1ecd nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd bi\u1ebfn gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 \u201c\u0111\u01b0a World Cup tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0\u201d c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh tan bi\u1ebfn.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- <strong>Colombia kh\u00f4ng thua</strong><br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: Colombia th\u1eafng 1-0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t kh\u00e1c</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- T\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f9ng l\u1eafm l\u00e0 9 (U 9)<br>\r\n- T\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c hi\u1ec7p 1 c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f9ng l\u1eafm l\u00e0 4 (U 4)<br>\r\n- T\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f9ng l\u1eafm l\u00e0 4 (U 4)<br>\r\n- S\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a Anh nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 2 (-1 1/2)<br>\r\n- S\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c hi\u1ec7p 1 c\u1ee7a Anh nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 1 (-1/2)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nLong Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng (TTVN)<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"850","checkdouble":"190293"},{"date":"17:33 03/07","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 21h00 ng\u00e0y 3/7 (World Cup 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/truc-tiep-thuy-sy-vs-thuy-dien.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018 l\u00fac 21h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 3/7.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018 l\u00fac 21h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 3/7.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Kh\u00f4ng xem \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, vui l\u00f2ng click t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP TH\u1ee4Y \u0110I\u1ec2N VS TH\u1ee4Y S\u1ef8<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"849","checkdouble":"190294"},{"date":"17:46 03/07","title":"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Colombia vs Anh: Kh\u00e1t v\u1ecdng 50 n\u0103m v\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i b\u00e1o th\u00f9","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/3/truoc-dai-chien-colombia-vs-anh-khat-vong-50-nam-va-co-hoi-bao-thu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam nay, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa \u0110T Colombia vs Anh t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 s\u1ebd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u, v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng mong \u0111\u1ee3i.\r\n</h2><h2>Tam S\u1ef1 v\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu search google c\u1ee5m t\u1eeb \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n <strong>&ldquo;It&rsquo;s Coming Home&rdquo;</strong> &ndash; b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn ng\u1eadp tr\u00e0n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0110T Anh, v\u1edbi Harry Kane gi\u01b0\u01a1ng cao chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap trong v\u00f2ng tay \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. &ldquo;Tr\u00e0o l\u01b0u&rdquo; n\u00e0y ng\u1eadp tr\u00e0n tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i Twitter trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y qua, n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 s\u1ebd \u0111em chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0ng v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 (coming home) k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1966.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, hashtag #itscominghome \u0111\u00e3 r\u00e2m ran ngay khi \u0110T th\u1eafng 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tunisia v\u00e0 Panama, cho th\u1ea5y ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111ang h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee9c n\u00e0o. \u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng G, nh\u01b0 ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Gareth Southgate \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea5u h\u00e0i khi b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1 \u0111\u00f2i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 2. Danny Rose b\u1ecf m\u1eb7c Adnan Januzaj ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh, \u0111\u1ec3 Tam S\u01b0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng &ldquo;ni\u1ec1m vui&rdquo; thua cu\u1ed9c.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng G, \u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e3 tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eed th\u1ea7n &ndash; n\u01a1i hi\u1ec7n h\u1eefu to\u00e0n &ldquo;th\u1ee9 d\u1eef&rdquo; nh\u01b0 Uruguay, Ph\u00e1p, Brazil v\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 B\u1ec9. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ea3 Argentina hay B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc, v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y may m\u1eafn v\u1edbi thuy\u1ebft \u00e2m m\u01b0u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Nh\u00ecn sang nh\u00e1nh b\u00ean kia, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p Nga/Croatia v\u00e0 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n/Th\u1ee5y S\u0129. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e0 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-nga-vs-tay-ban-nha-463-190102.html\" target=\"_blank\">T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc.</span><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Colombia vs Anh Gi\u1ea5c m\u1ed9ng b\u00e1 v\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 th\u1eddi c\u01a1 b\u00e1o th\u00f9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Colombia vs Anh Gi\u1ea5c m\u1ed9ng b\u00e1 v\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 th\u1eddi c\u01a1 b\u00e1o th\u00f9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/Colombia-vs-Anh-Giac-mong-ba-vuong-va-thoi-co-bao-thu-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110T Anh l\u1eadp s\u1eb5n k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\nHay n\u00f3i c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c, \u0110T Anh l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau th\u00edch cho m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t tham d\u1ef1 chung k\u1ebft. H\u1ecd \u0111ang \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u00e1 thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i, hay n\u00f3i ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c l\u00e0 nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u n\u1ebfu so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean \u1edf nh\u00e1nh t\u1eed th\u1ea7n. HLV Gareth Southgate \u0111\u00e3 cho g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng s\u1ee9c \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc, v\u00e0 \u0111ang &ldquo;rung \u0111\u00f9i&rdquo; ch\u1edd th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c L\u0110B\u0110 Anh (FA) giao nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i Harry Kane v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111ang \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng t\u01b0\u01a1i s\u00e1ng h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Tr\u00ean l\u00fd thuy\u1ebft, h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n, \u0110T n\u00e0o l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i &ldquo;l\u00ea l\u1ebft&rdquo; khi tr\u1ea3i qua to\u00e0n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1nh l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 ch\u1eef &ldquo;Nh\u01b0ng&rdquo; r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ecdi k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 <strong>li\u1ec7u \u0110T Anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eb7t ch\u00e2n v\u00e0o b\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ee9 nh\u1ea5t, \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110T Colombia v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam nay hay kh\u00f4ng?</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">X\u00e9t v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng quan l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Colombia s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i l\u1edbn khi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/colombia-nua-mung-nua-lo-ve-james-rodriguez-truoc-vong-18-469-190072.html\" target=\"_blank\">James Rodriguez b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n</span>. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Bayern Munich c\u00f3 k\u1ecbp g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o 100% &ndash; nh\u01b0 c\u00e1i c\u00e1ch James r\u1eddi s\u00e2n ch\u1ec9 sau 30 ph\u00fat tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Senegal \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Tam S\u01b0 t\u1eadp d\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u1ea1i v\u0169 kh\u00ed l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh &ndash; nh\u1eefng pha d\u00e0n x\u1ebfp \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t. Th\u1eadt may, Colombia kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ec3u nh\u01b0 Tunisia hay Panama, \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Southgate d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea1t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Nam M\u1ef9 c\u0169ng c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 nguy hi\u1ec3m \u1edf ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng n\u00e0y, trung v\u1ec7 Yerry Mina \u0111\u1ebfn nay \u0111\u00e3 ghi 2 b\u00e0n t\u1eeb \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Colombia vs Anh\" title=\"Colombia vs Anh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/eng.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh, nh\u01b0ng li\u1ec7u Tam S\u01b0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Colombia?</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>V\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf c\u1ee7a Colombia<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, tr\u00e1i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111ang n\u1eb1m <strong>&ldquo;\u0111\u1ebfm cua trong l\u1ed7&rdquo;</strong>, Colombia ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. H\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ngh\u0129 xa h\u01a1n, b\u1edfi tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0110T Anh c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i trong nh\u1eefng pha b\u00f3ng ch\u1ebft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Davinson Sanchez kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Harry Kane &ndash; ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Tottenham Hotspur. 1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Premier League d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u, nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng \u00edt \u0111\u1ec3 Sanchez t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n anh, v\u00e0 s\u1ebd l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn Harry Kane t\u1ecbt ng\u00f2i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTi\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3, s\u1ebd l\u00e0 2 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tr\u1ea3 th\u00f9 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao Colombia &ndash; Juan Cuadrado v\u00e0 Radamel Falcao. C\u1ea3 2 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng tr\u1ea3i qua nh\u1eefng n\u0103m th\u00e1ng \u0111\u00e1ng qu\u00ean trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p, trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Chelsea v\u00e0 Man United. V\u1edbi c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n M\u00e3nh h\u1ed5, anh th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n \u0111\u00e1 cho c\u1ea3 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eb3ng n\u01a1i n\u00e0o th\u00e8m r\u01b0\u1edbc nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n 1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Falcao va Cuadrado\" title=\"Falcao v\u00e0 Cuadrado\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/cao.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Falcao v\u00e0 Cuadrado \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh trong tr\u1eadn Colombia vs Anh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\nTr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Monaco, Falcao l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n b\u1ea3n n\u0103ng s\u00e1t th\u1ee7, v\u00e0 g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng C\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c \u0111i t\u1edbi b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League. V\u1edbi Cuadrado, sau khi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Chelsea, anh \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Juventus theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n, v\u00e0 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadp mua \u0111\u1ee9t.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u1ea3 2 s\u1ebd xem Premier League nh\u01b0 l\u00e0 n\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn. \u0110\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i ngo\u00e0i 30, g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 c\u1ea3 Cuadrado l\u1eabn Falcao s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i &ldquo;b\u00e1o th\u00f9&rdquo; gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch ch\u00e2n ch\u00ednh &ndash; nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Mohamed Salah \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Colombia vs Anh v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam nay s\u1ebd l\u00e0 th\u1eddi c\u01a1 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 2 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh mong ch\u1edd gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u0111\u00e3 h\u01a1n n\u1eeda th\u1ebf k\u1ef7 (52 n\u0103m), trong khi Colombia ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 v\u00e0ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ea1 m\u00e0n v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup n\u0103m nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-anh-vs-colombia-va-du-doan-soi-keo-colombia-vs-anh-421-190293.html\">Nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u1eddi cho c\u1ea7u \u0111inh Anh vs Colombia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dong-doi-o-spurs-san-sang-quyet-chien-voi-harry-kane-tai-vong-18-421-190283.html\">\u0110\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf Spurs s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng quy\u1ebft chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Harry Kane t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/gap-dt-anh-la-co-hoi-de-falcao-chung-to-minh-421-190282.html\">G\u1eb7p \u0110T Anh l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Falcao ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/rooney-tuyen-anh-co-the-mo-mong-o-world-cup-nay-421-190252.html\">Rooney: Tuy\u1ec3n Anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u01a1 m\u1ed9ng \u1edf World Cup n\u00e0y</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/southgate-dt-anh-se-khong-bi-loai-soc-nhu-o-euro-2016-469-190250.html\">Southgate: \u0110T Anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i s\u1ed1c nh\u01b0 \u1edf Euro 2016</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-colombia-vs-anh-1h00-ngay-47-co-den-tay-lieu-co-phat-421-190241.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Colombia vs Anh (1h00 ng\u00e0y 4/7): C\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn tay, li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 ph\u1ea5t?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; TTVN&nbsp;</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"848","checkdouble":"190295"},{"date":"10:23 03/07","title":"Thua \u0111au Brazil, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Mexico tr\u00e1ch nhau kh\u00f4ng h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/thua-dau-brazil-nguoi-mexico-trach-nhau-khong-het-minh-o-vong-bang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Rafael Marquez ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi Mexico \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh n\u00e9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u201ccon ng\u00e1o \u1ed9p\u201d n\u00e0y v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color: rgb(17, 17, 17);\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Brazil nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t, t\u1eeb tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ebfn b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh gi\u00e0 d\u01a1, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao, Mexico \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh kh\u1ecfi \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018, qua \u0111\u00f3 tr\u1ea3i qua l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 7 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp ch\u1ecbu \u0111\u1ef1ng c\u00e1i d\u1edbp l\u1ed7i h\u1eb9n v\u1edbi v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.</span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Brazil 2-0 Mexico El Tri tr\u00e1ch nhau v\u00ec m\u1ea5t ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Brazil 2-0 Mexico El Tri tr\u00e1ch nhau v\u00ec m\u1ea5t ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/thua-dau-brazil-nguoi-mexico-trach-nhau-khong-het-minh-o-vong-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mexico \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Brazil n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 quan \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">D\u1eabu v\u1eady n\u00f3i g\u00ec th\u00ec n\u00f3i, b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Mexico c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n bi\u1ebft t\u1ef1 tr\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh khi th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u1ee7 quan \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i s\u1edbm g\u1eb7p h\u1ea1n nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y. Ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n B\u1eafc M\u1ef9 l\u1ea1i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd nh\u1eadn th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i 0-3 d\u01b0\u1edbi tay Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, qua \u0111\u00f3 \u201cnh\u01b0\u1eddng\u201d m\u1ed9t Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 d\u1ec5 th\u1edf h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u cho \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Rafael Marquez sau tr\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-brazil-vs-mexico-463-190202.html\" target=\"_blank\">d\u01b0 \u00e2m Brazil 2-0 Mexico</span>: \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 t\u01b0\u1edfng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1ng ra c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfm ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh n\u00e9 Brazil \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc qu\u00fd b\u00e1u cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, r\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p ch\u1ee7 quan v\u00e0 b\u1ecf d\u1edf nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\u201d<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Brazil, chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c 2-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c gi\u00fap Selecao nu\u00f4i d\u01b0\u1ee1ng hy v\u1ecdng v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0ng th\u1ee9 s\u00e1u trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0. \u1ede v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Tite s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 B\u1ec9, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 v\u1eeba l\u00e0m n\u00ean cu\u1ed9c l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-diem-nhan-ngay-neymar-toa-sang-giup-brazil-ha-mexico-20-421-190231.html\">4 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n d\u01b0 \u00e2m Brazil 2-0 Mexico\u00a0</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-brazil-20-mexico-gia-tri-cua-neymar-khong-chi-o-nhung-ban-thang-421-190245.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Brazil 2-0 Mexico: Gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Neymar kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u1edf nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/brazil-20-mexico-xung-danh-nguoi-dan-duong-cua-world-cup-421-190244.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Brazil 2-0 Mexico: X\u1ee9ng danh \u201cng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng\u201d c\u1ee7a World Cup</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"color:#111111\">Gia Khoa (TTVN)</span></strong><span style=\"color:#111111\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"847","checkdouble":"190256"},{"date":"09:29 03/07","title":"\u0110\u00f2n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ti\u00eau di\u1ec7t \"Samurai xanh\" c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9: S\u1ef1 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p tinh t\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Lukaku","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/don-quyet-dinh-tieu-diet-samurai-xanh-cua-bi-su-dong-gop-tinh-te-cua-lukaku.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>S\u00e1t th\u1ee7 Lukaku d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u00f4ng s\u1ee9c c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0o ph\u00fat ch\u00f3t v\u00e0 c\u00f3 v\u00e9 v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd th\u1ee9 5 (cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng) \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 1/8 \u0111\u00eam qua, \u0110T B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh m\u00e0n ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ec3 \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 3-2, gi\u00e0nh l\u1ea5y chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng si\u00eau k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Lukaku g\u00f3p v\u00e0o b\u00e0n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 3-2 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Lukaku g\u00f3p v\u00e0o b\u00e0n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 3-2 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/3-thomas-meunier-makes-his-run-copy-1530569049657107471436.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Lukaku ch\u1ea1y ch\u1ed7 m\u1edf ra kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng cho Meunier.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKevin De Bruyne ph\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng, Meunier c\u0103ng ngang cho Chadli b\u0103ng v\u00e0o d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m. Nh\u01b0ng c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u1eefa \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi c\u00f4ng tr\u1ea1ng l\u1edbn trong t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y l\u00e0 Romelu Lukaku, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat \u0111\u00e3 \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng trong ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn th\u1eddi gian.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ee3t ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Courtois b\u1eaft d\u00ednh tr\u00e1i b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ee7a Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. Kevin De Bruyne d\u1eabn b\u00f3ng c\u1ef1c nhanh v\u1ec1 n\u1eeda s\u00e2n b\u00ean kia. Nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 hai b\u00ean l\u00fac n\u00e0y kh\u00e1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng. Song t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ea7n ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i cho B\u1ec9 khi Lukaku ch\u1ea1y ch\u1ed7 r\u1ea5t kh\u00e9o \u0111\u1ec3 thu h\u00fat s\u1ef1 ch\u00fa \u00fd c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, qua \u0111\u00f3 m\u1edf ra kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng l\u1edbn b\u00ean c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKevin De Bruyne qu\u00e1 hi\u1ec3u \u00fd ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i n\u00ean \u0111\u1ea9y tr\u00e1i b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t v\u1eeba t\u1ea7m b\u0103ng l\u00ean c\u1ee7a Meunier. Sau \u0111\u00f3 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 c\u0103ng ngang s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tung ra nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u00edch ng\u1eafm l\u00e0 ai?\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lukaku tiep tuc chay cho hut nguoi.\" title=\"Lukaku ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u1ea1y ch\u1ed7 h\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/4-meunier-crosses-the-ball-in-copy-1530569049658220302504.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Lukaku ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u1ea1y ch\u1ed7 h\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nLukaku ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u00e1m s\u00e1t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c di chuy\u1ec3n, khi\u1ebfn Hasebe kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1m theo ch\u00e2n s\u00fat kho\u00e1c \u00e1o M.U. Meunier \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y c\u00f3 2 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tung ra pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00ean quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u00e1i b\u00f3ng c\u1eaft ngang v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eb9p, ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n n\u1eb1m trong t\u1ea7m ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Lukaku. Nh\u01b0ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o sinh n\u0103m 1993 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd gi\u01a1 ch\u00e2n l\u00ean l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00e1c gi\u1ea3, \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00f3ng l\u1ecdt ra ph\u00eda sau v\u00e0 s\u1ee9c kh\u00e1ng c\u1ef1 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tan bi\u1ebfn. Chadli \u0111\u00e3 b\u0103ng l\u00ean v\u1eeba k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec7m b\u00f3ng tung l\u01b0\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ngh\u1eb9t th\u1edf cho B\u1ec9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u01a1n 90 ph\u00fat nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n h\u01a1n ch\u1ee5c gi\u00e2y v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a Lukaku \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf. <br>\r\n<h2>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: B\u1ec9 3-2 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text - align:center; width: 100 %; padding: 20px 0; \"><video class=\"hlsvideoobj\" data-src=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/DRM/HLS/201807/274945/master.m3u8\" controls=\"\"></video></div>\r\n<h2>C\u00e1c tin b\u00e0i kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 3-2 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-nhat-ban-tiec-vi-khong-thang-bi-465-190233.html\">HLV Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n kh\u00f4ng ng\u1edd B\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng s\u1eafc b\u00e9n \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ebf</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/eden-hazard-thua-nhan-bi-tung-run-so-nhat-ban-465-190236.html\">Eden Hazard th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn B\u1ec9 t\u1eebng run s\u1ee3 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n khi b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thong-ke-khong-the-bo-qua-tran-bi-32-nhat-ban-421-190237.html\">Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 3-2 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-roberto-martinez-phat-bieu-ve-tran-bi-vs-nhat-ban-421-190238.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u1ea7n k\u1ef3 v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, HLV B\u1ec9 n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-dieu-rut-ra-sau-man-nguoc-dong-kho-tin-cua-bi-truoc-nhat-ban-421-190239.html\">4 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau m\u00e0n ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng kh\u00f3 tin c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-bi-32-nhat-ban-quy-do-no-samurai-loi-cam-on-421-190243.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m B\u1ec9 3-2 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n: Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf n\u1ee3 Samurai l\u1eddi c\u1ea3m \u01a1n!</span></div>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"846","checkdouble":"190257"},{"date":"10:31 03/07","title":"Modric \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Dalic tin t\u01b0\u1edfng d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng penalty tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110an M\u1ea1ch","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/an-tuong-kieu-chao-cua-chien-binh-dzyuba.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110ang chinh chi\u1ebfn t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, nh\u01b0ng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a \u0110T B\u1ec9 - Thibaut Courtois mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Madrid v\u00e0 \u00fap m\u1edf v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nCourtois \u0111\u00f2i ra \u0111i b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u01b0a gia h\u1ea1n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi Chelsea, v\u00e0 c\u00f3 v\u1ebb c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Courtois \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng r\u1eddi London ngay m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Hi\u1ec7n nay, Real Madrid \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y nh\u1ea5t, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb b\u1ecf m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau Alisson Becker v\u00ec th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2019, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Chelsea bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i chia tay Courtois ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a anh s\u1ee5t gi\u1ea3m. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n sinh n\u0103m 1992 \u0111\u00e3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t th\u00edch s\u1ed1ng \u1edf th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 London, <strong>v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Madrid n\u1eefa</strong>&rdquo; &ndash; Courtois ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u. &ldquo;\u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 c\u00e1c con t\u00f4i s\u1ed1ng \u1edf Madrid, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ea7n ch\u00fang. B\u00ecnh t\u0129nh n\u00e0o, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a t\u00f4i s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn gia \u0111\u00ecnh r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, v\u00e0 t\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u00e0m b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ea7n g\u0169i nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Courtois mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Madrid ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c\" title=\"Courtois\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/courtois-nang-nac-doi-chuyen-toi-madrid-vi-mot-dieu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Courtois&nbsp;mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Madrid ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n th\u1ea3o lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ngay b\u00e2y gi\u1edd. Ch\u00fang ta h\u00e3y c\u00f9ng ch\u1edd xem \u0111\u1ebfn khi World Cup 2018 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i. \u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb, v\u00e0 <strong>t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3&rdquo;</strong> &ndash; Courtois cho bi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Courtois v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0110T B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n trong tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u si\u00eau k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh, khi h\u1ecd l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng d\u00f9 b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2 b\u00e0n. Trong \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Chelsea c\u0169ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p l\u1edbn v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd, khi anh ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, v\u00e0 nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Brazil trong tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. \u1ede \u0111\u00e2y, Courtois s\u1ebd c\u00f3 d\u1ecbp ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi Casemiro v\u00e0 Marcelo, \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau Courtois mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Madrid tr\u1edf n\u00ean g\u1ea7n h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/don-quyet-dinh-tieu-diet-samurai-xanh-cua-bi-su-dong-gop-tinh-te-cua-lukaku-421-190257.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/don-quyet-dinh-tieu-diet-samurai-xanh-cua-bi-su-dong-gop-tinh-te-cua-lukaku.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/don-quyet-dinh-tieu-diet-samurai-xanh-cua-bi-su-dong-gop-tinh-te-cua-lukaku-421-190257.html\">\u0110\u00f2n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ti\u00eau di\u1ec7t Samurai xanh c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9: S\u1ef1 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p tinh t\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Lukaku</span><br>\r\nS\u00e1t th\u1ee7 Lukaku d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u00f4ng s\u1ee9c c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0o ph\u00fat ch\u00f3t v\u00e0 c\u00f3 v\u00e9 v\u00e0o...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-bi-vs-nhat-ban-461-190228.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/Bi-vuot-qua-Nhat-vao-tu-ket.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-bi-vs-nhat-ban-461-190228.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: B\u1ec9 3-2 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n (V\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nB\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 0-2 v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7p 2 ch\u1ec9 v\u1eeba m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u, nh\u01b0ng B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1eadt ng\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf \u0111\u00fang v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-dieu-rut-ra-sau-man-nguoc-dong-kho-tin-cua-bi-truoc-nhat-ban-421-190239.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/Thong-ke-Bi-vs-Nhat-Ban---Vong-18-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-dieu-rut-ra-sau-man-nguoc-dong-kho-tin-cua-bi-truoc-nhat-ban-421-190239.html\">4 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau m\u00e0n ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng kh\u00f3 tin c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span><br>\r\nNh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n d\u00f9 d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 2-0 nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ec3 thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-3 qua \u0111\u00f3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e9 v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft cho \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. C\u00f9ng nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u1ea5n...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"845","checkdouble":"190258"},{"date":"10:49 03/07","title":"Vieira: \"Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/30/vieira-phap-se-vao-chung-ket-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Patrick Vieira kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina v\u00e0 r\u1ed9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</h2><h2>Ph\u00e1p th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Argentina</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Didier Deschamps \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o phong \u0111\u1ed9 sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina \u1edf v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00f4m th\u1ee9 B\u1ea3y v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKylian Mbappe \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadp m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap v\u00e0 ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 penalty tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina. V\u00e0 v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a sao tr\u1ebb n\u00e0y, Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eb3ng ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p Uruguay.</div>\r\n<h2>C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u \u1edf World Cup 2018\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Vieira tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Vieira tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/30/Vieira-tin-tuong-Phap-se-vao-chung-ket-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Vieira tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Patrick Vieira cho r\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t x\u00fac t\u00e1c c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 Ph\u00e1p b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 t\u1ea1i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span> v\u00e0 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<em><br>\r\n\u201cB\u00e2y gi\u1edd, ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch World Cup c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p theo m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c. C\u0169ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi, t\u00f4i k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n ch\u00fang ta.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cD\u1eabu sao, t\u00f4i c\u0169ng ngh\u0129 l\u00e0 ch\u00fang ta h\u01a1i kh\u1eaft khe v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 s\u1ebd c\u00f3 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ed1t t\u1edbi ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay. H\u1ecd c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 v\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00f3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 mong mu\u1ed1n Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup. Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 tin h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u. H\u1ecd ch\u01a1i t\u1ef1 do h\u01a1n. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 Ph\u00e1p kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTheo quan \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup n\u0103m nay\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 n\u0103m th\u1ee9 2 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p l\u1ecdt t\u1edbi v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup. Tuy nhi\u00ean, con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Uruguay, Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 m\u1ed9t trong hai \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 Brazil ho\u1eb7c B\u1ec9 \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 \u0110T\u00a0Ph\u00e1p:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sao-tuyen-phap-trai-long-ve-sieu-pham-cuu-roi-chien-thang-argentina-421-190134.html\">Sao tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p tr\u1ea3i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee9u r\u1ed7i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng Argentina</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/antoine-griezmann-phu-phang-voi-diego-godin-421-190167.html\">Antoine Griezmann ph\u0169 ph\u00e0ng v\u1edbi Diego Godin</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"844","checkdouble":"190260"},{"date":"11:08 03/07","title":"Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c: Monaco chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a l\u00f2 La Masia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/chinh-thuc-monaco-chieu-mo-robert-navarro-than-dong-cua-lo-la-masia.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Monaco ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0o l\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb khi chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Robert Navarro c\u1ee7a Barcelona.</h2><h2>Monaco chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Robert Navarro</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Robert Navarro \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00eda Monaco \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u201cni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 ti\u1ebfp theo\u201d trong bu\u1ed5i l\u1ec5 ra m\u1eaft v\u1eeba qua. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 16 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 C\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u0103m nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cMonaco l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. H\u1ecd t\u1eadp trung r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u cho c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cM\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn l\u00ean ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 v\u01b0\u01a1n t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p m\u1edbi t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Monaco ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0o l\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c Monaco chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Robert Navarro, th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u00f2 La Masia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c Monaco chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Robert Navarro, th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u00f2 La Masia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/chinh-thuc-monaco-chieu-mo-robert-navarro-than-dong-cua-lo-la-masia.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Monaco chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Robert Navarro t\u1eeb Barcelona</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 mang v\u1ec1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng cho Monaco \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2016/17 \u0111\u00e3 ra \u0111i g\u1ea7n h\u1ebft. Kylian Mbappe c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch Paris Saint-Germain. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Bernardo Silva v\u00e0 Benjamin Mendy \u0111\u1ec1u gia nh\u1eadp Manchester City.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 th\u00e1o ch\u1ea1y c\u1ee7a Thomas Lemar, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi gia nh\u1eadp Atletico Madrid. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/nong-liverpool-bat-ngo-chinh-thuc-chieu-mo-tien-ve-fabinho-tu-monaco-172-187236.html\" target=\"_blank\">Fabinho c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1n cho Liverpool</span> v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c, Monaco \u0111\u00e3 d\u00f9ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0. H\u1ecd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Willem Geubbels t\u1eeb Lyon\u00a0 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 20 tri\u1ec7u euro h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh Samuel Grandsir c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111em v\u1ec1 theo m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 5 n\u0103m \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nRobert Navarro l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean th\u1ee9 3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn s\u00e2n Stade Louis II h\u00e8 2018. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 16 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y ch\u01a1i n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong vai tr\u00f2 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc. C\u0169ng nh\u1edd l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1eadm ch\u1ea5t la tinh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh m\u00e0 Navarro c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t bi\u1ec7t danh \u201cRobertinho\u201d \u1edf l\u00f2 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o La Masia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Monaco:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/dai-gia-la-liga-chinh-thuc-so-huu-thomas-lemar-voi-gia-khung-180-188349.html\">\u0110\u1ea1i gia La Liga ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c s\u1edf h\u1eefu Thomas Lemar v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 kh\u1ee7ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-gia-nhap-cuoc-dua-gianh-sao-khung-monaco-180-187985.html\">Barca gia nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh sao kh\u1ee7ng Monaco</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"843","checkdouble":"190262"}]}